        "subtitle": "Simulated trends in AI, finance, sustainability, and fitness for forecasting and",
        "description": "This synthetic dataset mimics 2024 trends across technology, finance, and sustainability. It includes:  \n- **10,000 records** with timestamps (Jan 2023 - Dec 2024).  \n- **Key metrics**: Weekly popularity, sentiment scores, growth rates, and regional data.  \n- **Use Cases**: Time-series forecasting, sentiment analysis, and trend clustering.  \n\n*Disclaimer: Data is entirely synthetic and not based on real-world observations.*  \n\n=== About this file ===\n\nAbout this file\nUpdate Frequency: Static (one-time simulation)\nDataset Size: 10,000 rows (~1.5 MB)\nGenerated With: Python (Faker, Pandas, NumPy)\n\n\n=== Columns & descriptions ===\n\ntrend_id: Unique identifier for each trend.\ntrend_name: Name of the trend (e.g., \"AI Agents\").\ncategory: Trend category (Tech/Finance/Sustainability).\ndate: Date of record (YYYY-MM-DD).\nweekly_interest: Normalized popularity score (0-100).\nregion: Geographic origin of the trend.\nsentiment: Social media sentiment (-1 to +1)\nrelated_brands: top brands associated with the trend\ngrowth_rate: Month-over-month change in interest (%).\nforecast_2025: Predicted interest score for 2025 (0-100).\n",
